												<b class="fn">pmdr</b> <span class="says">says:</span>					</div><!-- .comment-author -->

					<div class="comment-metadata">
						<a href="http://mako.cc/copyrighteous/google-has-most-of-my-email-because-it-has-all-of-yours#comment-19539">
							<time datetime="2014-05-13T09:50:05+00:00">
								May 13, 2014 at 09:50							</time>
