				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>Even though GMail may have a significant portion of my emails, they don&#8217;t have it in one place.  If presented with a request for all of my emails, they couldn&#8217;t supply anyone with my inbox.  It is doubtful, that they would be forced to scan everyone&#8217;s email box for messages that include me.</p>
