					<p><cite>&#8230;the fact that I spend hundreds of dollars a year and hours of work to host my own email server, &#8230;</cite><br />
What makes this so expensive?  Doesn&#8217;t seem very compatible with ideas of easily/cheaply hosting for yourself, like Freedombox&#8230;</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

				<div class="reply">
					<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/copyrighteous/google-has-most-of-my-email-because-it-has-all-of-yours?replytocom=115322#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("div-comment-115322", "115322", "respond", "2527")'>Reply</a>				</div><!-- .reply -->
